{"tid":1997053,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇絲打試過流啡色嘢","createTime":"2020-05-01T11:18:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-02T18:08:20.000Z","uid":325029,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"e63cbd537d930ef5be473a4da38288c8181aa4e2","tid":1997053,"uid":325029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T11:18:28.000Z","msg":"今個月11號嚟咗m<br />\n但由26號開始有啲啡色嘢流出嚟<br />\n又唔係m血 <br />\n但佢流又唔多 只係少少<br />\n有時一pat 有時幾滴<br />\n有啲驚會唔會入面有啲咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我上年年中試過又係有啲啡色嘢流出嚟<br />\n又唔係m血<br />\n但唔太記得流咗幾耐<br />\n應該都有一段時間<br />\n之後我去咗睇家庭醫生<br />\n佢就比咗2星期嘅調經藥<br />\n食完之後嘅下個月正常返<br />\n但再之後嘅月份都係唔太準<br />\n<br />\n雖然本身次次嚟m都會遲<br />\n有啲幾日<br />\n有時一星期<br />\n有試一個月<br />\n<br />\n有時又會谷m<br />\n肚脹 胸部脹痛<br />\n最後先嚟m<br />\n<br />\n一直都好想去睇中醫調理身體<br />\n但就係唔知睇邊個好<br />\n又唔知邊個有用"},{"pid":"1ba95893fee4e98115c47ba211535363886c9539","tid":1997053,"uid":144,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T11:21:24.000Z","msg":"芝士?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60581372384fc84ee702c6b8a0d50885cda13ac0","tid":1997053,"uid":40272,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T11:24:05.000Z","msg":"個閪一定好臭"},{"pid":"3ef558ca606f251cce221f71e46aa37dc752f5d4","tid":1997053,"uid":162268,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T11:27:06.000Z","msg":"諗起都覺得臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e587d8f939e3c8ca294613ad868d7ba45591a67","tid":1997053,"uid":59244,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T11:27:57.000Z","msg":"我都係！有聽人講過話有咗都會咁，今日驗咗，又無中<br />\n身體真係好差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c436f1f247485706fb065929ab958dd9163336e","tid":1997053,"uid":38707,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T11:30:49.000Z","msg":"去睇婦科啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=